data.actual_result: Gives out an Error Message "Category does not exist"
data.expected_result: Voice Channel Settings Should be Saved and Updated
data.short_description: Settings On Uncategorized Voice Channels Can't Be Updated , Instead Gives Out An Error Message "Category does not exist"
data.steps_to_repro: - Click on Any Uncategorized Voice Channel you have Permissions of editing . - Go to "Channel Settings" . - Modify Any of The Channel Settings ,For Example ,Name , Bitrate etc.. - Press The Save Icon To Save Changes .
